claim: Stranger Things includes an antagonist who is able to influence a physical system without physical interaction.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Psychokinesis  (  from Greek ψυχή `` mind '' and κίνησις `` movement ''  )  , or telekinesis  (  from τῆλε `` far off '' and κίνησις `` movement ''  )  , is an alleged psychic ability allowing a person to influence a physical system without physical interaction .
